{"tha-ap535:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap535:0.2":"Kaccayanavagga ","tha-ap535:0.3":"Mahakappinattheraapadana ","tha-ap535:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap535:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap535:1.3":"Udito ajatakase, ","tha-ap535:1.4":"raviva saradambare. ","tha-ap535:2.1":"Vacanabhaya bodheti, ","tha-ap535:2.2":"veneyyapadumani so; ","tha-ap535:2.3":"Kilesapankam soseti, ","tha-ap535:2.4":"matiramsihi nayako. ","tha-ap535:3.1":"Titthiyanam yase hanti, ","tha-ap535:3.2":"khajjotabha yatha ravi; ","tha-ap535:3.3":"Saccatthabham pakaseti, ","tha-ap535:3.4":"ratanamva divakaro. ","tha-ap535:4.1":"Gunanam ayatibhuto, ","tha-ap535:4.2":"ratananamva sagaro; ","tha-ap535:4.3":"Pajjunnoriva bhutani, ","tha-ap535:4.4":"dhammameghena vassati. ","tha-ap535:5.1":"Akkhadasso tada asim, ","tha-ap535:5.2":"nagare hamsasavhaye; ","tha-ap535:5.3":"Upecca dhammamassosim, ","tha-ap535:5.4":"jalajuttamanamino. ","tha-ap535:6.1":"Ovadakassa bhikkhunam, ","tha-ap535:6.2":"savakassa katavino; ","tha-ap535:6.3":"Gunam pakasayantassa, ","tha-ap535:6.4":"tappayantassa me manam. ","tha-ap535:7.1":"Sutva patito sumano, ","tha-ap535:7.2":"nimantetva tathagatam; ","tha-ap535:7.3":"Sasissam bhojayitvana, ","tha-ap535:7.4":"tam thanamabhipatthayim. ","tha-ap535:8.1":"Tada hamsasamabhago, ","tha-ap535:8.2":"hamsadundubhinissano; ","tha-ap535:8.3":"‘Passathetam mahamattam, ","tha-ap535:8.4":"vinicchayavisaradam. ","tha-ap535:9.1":"Patitam padamule me, ","tha-ap535:9.2":"samuggatatanuruham; ","tha-ap535:9.3":"Jimutavannam pinamsam, ","tha-ap535:9.4":"pasannanayanananam. ","tha-ap535:10.1":"Parivarena mahata, ","tha-ap535:10.2":"rajayuttam mahayasam; ","tha-ap535:10.3":"Eso katavino thanam, ","tha-ap535:10.4":"pattheti muditasayo. ","tha-ap535:11.1":"Imina panipatena, ","tha-ap535:11.2":"cagena panidhihi ca; ","tha-ap535:11.3":"Kappasatasahassani, ","tha-ap535:11.4":"nupapajjati duggatim. ","tha-ap535:12.1":"Devesu devasobhaggam, ","tha-ap535:12.2":"manussesu mahantatam; ","tha-ap535:12.3":"Anubhotvana sesena, ","tha-ap535:12.4":"nibbanam papunissati. ","tha-ap535:13.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap535:13.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap535:13.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap535:13.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap535:14.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap535:14.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap535:14.3":"Kappino nama namena, ","tha-ap535:14.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap535:15.1":"Tatoham sukatam karam, ","tha-ap535:15.2":"katvana jinasasane; ","tha-ap535:15.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap535:15.4":"tusitam agamasaham. ","tha-ap535:16.1":"Devamanusarajjani, ","tha-ap535:16.2":"sataso anusasiya; ","tha-ap535:16.3":"Baranasiyamasanne, ","tha-ap535:16.4":"jato keniyajatiyam. ","tha-ap535:17.1":"Sahassaparivarena, ","tha-ap535:17.2":"sapajapatiko aham; ","tha-ap535:17.3":"Panca paccekabuddhanam, ","tha-ap535:17.4":"satani samupatthahim. ","tha-ap535:18.1":"Temasam bhojayitvana, ","tha-ap535:18.2":"pacchadamha ticivaram; ","tha-ap535:18.3":"Tato cuta mayam sabbe, ","tha-ap535:18.4":"ahumha tidasupaga. ","tha-ap535:19.1":"Puno sabbe manussattam, ","tha-ap535:19.2":"agamimha tato cuta; ","tha-ap535:19.3":"Kukkutamhi pure jata, ","tha-ap535:19.4":"himavantassa passato. ","tha-ap535:20.1":"Kappino namaham asim, ","tha-ap535:20.2":"rajaputto mahayaso; ","tha-ap535:20.3":"Sesamaccakule jata, ","tha-ap535:20.4":"mameva parivarayum. ","tha-ap535:21.1":"Maharajjasukham patto, ","tha-ap535:21.2":"sabbakamasamiddhima; ","tha-ap535:21.3":"Vanijehi samakkhatam, ","tha-ap535:21.4":"buddhuppadamaham sunim. ","tha-ap535:22.1":"‘Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap535:22.2":"asamo ekapuggalo; ","tha-ap535:22.3":"So pakaseti saddhammam, ","tha-ap535:22.4":"amatam sukhamuttamam. ","tha-ap535:23.1":"Suyutta tassa sissa ca, ","tha-ap535:23.2":"sumutta ca anasava’; ","tha-ap535:23.3":"Sutva nesam suvacanam, ","tha-ap535:23.4":"sakkaritvana vanije. ","tha-ap535:24.1":"Pahaya rajjam samacco, ","tha-ap535:24.2":"nikkhamim buddhamamako; ","tha-ap535:24.3":"Nadim disva mahacandam, ","tha-ap535:24.4":"puritam samatittikam. ","tha-ap535:25.1":"Appatittham analambam, ","tha-ap535:25.2":"duttaram sighavahinim; ","tha-ap535:25.3":"Gunam saritva buddhassa, ","tha-ap535:25.4":"sotthina samatikkamim. ","tha-ap535:26.1":"‘Bhavasotam sace buddho, ","tha-ap535:26.2":"tinno lokantagu vidu; ","tha-ap535:26.3":"Etena saccavajjena, ","tha-ap535:26.4":"gamanam me samijjhatu. ","tha-ap535:27.1":"Yadi santigamo maggo, ","tha-ap535:27.2":"mokkho caccantikam sukham; ","tha-ap535:27.3":"Etena saccavajjena, ","tha-ap535:27.4":"gamanam me samijjhatu. ","tha-ap535:28.1":"Sangho ce tinnakantaro, ","tha-ap535:28.2":"punnakkhetto anuttaro; ","tha-ap535:28.3":"Etena saccavajjena, ","tha-ap535:28.4":"gamanam me samijjhatu’. ","tha-ap535:29.1":"Saha kate saccavare, ","tha-ap535:29.2":"magga apagatam jalam; ","tha-ap535:29.3":"Tato sukhena uttinno, ","tha-ap535:29.4":"naditire manorame. ","tha-ap535:30.1":"Nisinnam addasam buddham, ","tha-ap535:30.2":"udentamva pabhankaram; ","tha-ap535:30.3":"Jalantam hemaselamva, ","tha-ap535:30.4":"diparukkhamva jotitam. ","tha-ap535:31.1":"Sasimva tarasahitam, ","tha-ap535:31.2":"savakehi purakkhatam; ","tha-ap535:31.3":"Vasavam viya vassantam, ","tha-ap535:31.4":"desanajaladantaram. ","tha-ap535:32.1":"Vanditvana sahamacco, ","tha-ap535:32.2":"ekamantamupavisim; ","tha-ap535:32.3":"Tato no asayam natva, ","tha-ap535:32.4":"buddho dhammamadesayi. ","tha-ap535:33.1":"Sutvana dhammam vimalam, ","tha-ap535:33.2":"avocumha mayam jinam; ","tha-ap535:33.3":"‘Pabbajehi mahavira, ","tha-ap535:33.4":"nibbindamha mayam bhave’. ","tha-ap535:34.1":"‘Svakkhato bhikkhave dhammo, ","tha-ap535:34.2":"dukkhantakaranaya vo; ","tha-ap535:34.3":"Caratha brahmacariyam’, ","tha-ap535:34.4":"iccaha munisattamo. ","tha-ap535:35.1":"Saha vacaya sabbepi, ","tha-ap535:35.2":"bhikkhuvesadhara mayam; ","tha-ap535:35.3":"Ahumha upasampanna, ","tha-ap535:35.4":"sotapanna ca sasane. ","tha-ap535:36.1":"Tato jetavanam gantva, ","tha-ap535:36.2":"anusasi vinayako; ","tha-ap535:36.3":"Anusittho jinenaham, ","tha-ap535:36.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap535:37.1":"Tato bhikkhusahassani, ","tha-ap535:37.2":"anusasimaham tada; ","tha-ap535:37.3":"Mamanusasanakara, ","tha-ap535:37.4":"tepi asum anasava. ","tha-ap535:38.1":"Jino tasmim gune tuttho, ","tha-ap535:38.2":"etadagge thapesi mam; ","tha-ap535:38.3":"Bhikkhuovadakanaggo, ","tha-ap535:38.4":"kappinoti mahajane. ","tha-ap535:39.1":"Satasahasse katam kammam, ","tha-ap535:39.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap535:39.3":"Pamutto saravegova, ","tha-ap535:39.4":"kilese jhapayim mama. ","tha-ap535:40.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap535:40.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap535:40.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap535:41.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap535:41.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap535:41.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap535:42.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap535:42.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap535:42.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap535:43.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mahakappino thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap535:44.1":"Mahakappinattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}